@10 = ~Greetings, I am Nathan.  I have recently arrived from Shadowdale. It was a long trek, but I wanted to get the most value I could from the items I had collected.~
@11 = ~ Athkatla is known as the richest city in all of Faerun, so I knew there would be adventurers about with the amount of coin I was looking for. Would you like to take a look at my wares? I have collected many artifacts from around the realms~
@12 = ~I would, please.~
@13 = ~No thank you, I'll pass.~
@14  = ~As you will.~
@15  = ~Come again!~
